item.description:
Lets all head back to Princeton Station to boogy and party to our band FOTF, its nice to give back to our establishment that treated us soo good when we needed them.. Also to make some new friends and welcome old ones. I will get there around 7:30ish early birds grab us some tables:), we know how to do this. Put in your reply so peeps know who you to look for, and yes I will make the intros then off to the dance floor for me.

Meet up signs will be on the tables in the lounge.
